  <h2>The Golden Hour</h2>
  <p>
    Photographers often talk about the "golden hour" - that brief period just after sunrise or before
    sunset when the light is soft, warm, and perfect for photography. But there's something even more
    special about the moments just before the sun appears.
  </p>

