  <h2>The Experience</h2>
  <p>
    This shot was taken after a challenging 3-hour hike in complete darkness. The cold was biting,
    but as the first light began to creep over the horizon, every moment of discomfort was forgotten.
    This is what landscape photography is all about - being in the right place at the right time.
  </p>

